IA_DECLARE_RETURNS_RETAINED_ON_PARAMETERS**\n- **COREMEDIA_USE_DERIVED_ENUMS_FOR_CONSTANTS**\n- **CMITEMCOUNT_MAX**\n- **COREMEDIA_CMBASECLASS_VERSION_IS_POINTER_ALIGNED**\n- **COREMEDIA_DECLARE_RELEASES_ARGUMENT**\n- **COREMEDIA_FALSE**\n- **COREMEDIA_TRUE**\n- **COREMEDIA_USE_ALIGNED_CMBASECLASS_VERSION**\n- **CMTIMEBASE_USE_SOURCE_TERMINOLOGY**\n- **COREMEDIA_DECLARE_RETURNS_RETAINED_BLOCK**\n\n",
